	<p>Field Associates, P.C. is a multi-disciplined consulting engineering firm, centrally located in Nassau County.  We specialize in Environmental Engineering, Electrical, Mechanical (HVAC), Plumbing, Construction Management and Design Services. We were established in February 1975.</p>

